					m_sNote = ""
					m_commentText = "The same animgraph is reused for all throwables.\n\nI just save a copy of the graph with the _grenade_type enum\'s default value set to different values. The flash grenade serves as the base.\n\nThis saves me the trouble of managing several copies of the graph (while making sure whoever uses throwables doesn\'t have to set the variable themselves).\n\nIs it silly\? Yes.\nDoes it work\? Unfortunately, yes."
